00:18:03.120 --> 00:18:04.390
I

00:18:06.000 --> 00:18:08.149
feel

00:18:13.149 --> 00:18:13.159
dry

00:18:18.870 --> 00:18:18.880
and

00:18:23.750 --> 00:18:23.760
the

00:18:27.240 --> 00:18:29.590
Lord

00:18:35.590 --> 00:18:35.600
tells

00:18:40.520 --> 00:18:41.789
me, 'Brandon, your Word

00:18:41.799 --> 00:18:45.350
level's low.

00:18:45.360 --> 00:18:47.430
You haven't been in the Word

00:18:47.440 --> 00:18:50.190
enough.'You've

00:18:50.200 --> 00:18:51.590
got to fill yourself with the

00:18:51.600 --> 00:18:52.950
Holy Ghost,

00:18:52.950 --> 00:18:52.960
pray

00:18:52.960 --> 00:18:54.510
in the

00:18:54.520 --> 00:18:56.510
spirit, and jump in

00:18:56.520 --> 00:18:59.110
that river.

00:19:13.630 --> 00:19:13.640
I

00:19:29.799 --> 00:19:32.990
have

00:19:33.000 --> 00:19:34.830
the same Holy Spirit inside of

00:19:34.830 --> 00:19:34.840
me

00:19:34.840 --> 00:19:37.430
as you do; I just

00:19:37.440 --> 00:19:40.430
choose to operate in it more. He

00:19:40.430 --> 00:19:40.440
is

00:19:40.440 --> 00:19:42.950
no

00:19:42.960 --> 00:19:46.149
respecter

00:19:46.159 --> 00:19:49.029
of

00:19:49.039 --> 00:19:51.549
persons,

00:19:56.600 --> 00:19:59.230
but He is a respecter of faith.

00:19:59.240 --> 00:20:01.750
If you

00:20:01.760 --> 00:20:03.710
aren't

00:20:03.720 --> 00:20:05.630
seeing miracles, it's

00:20:20.919 --> 00:20:22.669
because you're ignorant of the

00:20:22.669 --> 00:20:22.679
Word. The Bible

00:20:22.679 --> 00:20:25.950
says that by

00:20:25.960 --> 00:20:29.510
His stripes we are healed. When the evening was

00:20:38.919 --> 00:20:41.070
come, they brought

00:20:41.080 --> 00:20:42.950
Him many who were possessed,

00:20:42.960 --> 00:20:45.390
and He cast out the spirits with

00:20:45.400 --> 00:20:48.590
His word and healed all who were

00:20:48.600 --> 00:20:50.830
oppressed.

00:21:14.159 --> 00:21:16.350
Do

00:21:16.360 --> 00:21:19.590
you believe Jesus

00:21:23.950 --> 00:21:23.960
will

00:21:28.000 --> 00:21:30.789
do it for

00:21:30.799 --> 00:21:34.909
you?

00:21:34.919 --> 00:21:38.310
Most people believe He can,

00:21:46.480 --> 00:21:48.789
but do you

00:21:48.799 --> 00:21:50.390
believe He has compassion on you? The woman with the issue of blood believed it,

00:21:56.070 --> 00:21:56.080
and

00:22:03.600 --> 00:22:05.870
her faith

00:22:08.120 --> 00:22:09.590
made

00:22:12.360 --> 00:22:16.029
her

00:22:16.039 --> 00:22:20.549
whole.

00:22:23.640 --> 00:22:27.669
Jesus Christ is the same

00:22:27.679 --> 00:22:30.669
yesterday, today, and forever.

00:22:49.799 --> 00:22:53.190
We receive

00:22:53.200 --> 00:22:55.870
salvation by grace through

00:22:55.880 --> 00:22:58.909
faith,

00:22:58.919 --> 00:23:01.070
and

00:23:01.080 --> 00:23:02.950
it

00:23:02.960 --> 00:23:05.149
takes

00:23:05.159 --> 00:23:06.110
the

00:23:06.120 --> 00:23:08.310
same

00:23:08.320 --> 00:23:10.470
amount

00:23:10.480 --> 00:23:12.789
of

00:23:12.799 --> 00:23:14.590
faith

00:23:14.590 --> 00:23:14.600
to

00:23:14.600 --> 00:23:17.669
believe for

00:23:17.679 --> 00:23:19.190
healing.

00:23:20.960 --> 00:23:22.950
You

00:23:25.400 --> 00:23:26.870
have

00:23:28.200 --> 00:23:29.669
to be

00:24:07.640 --> 00:24:10.029
like a bulldog on a bone; I'm

00:24:10.039 --> 00:24:13.390
not letting go of what He promised me.

00:26:05.120 --> 00:26:08.269
Father, I thank you for every

00:26:08.269 --> 00:26:08.279
person

00:26:08.279 --> 00:26:10.110
represented

00:26:10.120 --> 00:26:13.389
here.

00:26:20.200 --> 00:26:22.430
I call healing over their bodies right

00:26:22.440 --> 00:26:24.830
now in the name of Jesus. I command

00:26:24.840 --> 00:26:27.669
sickness

00:26:27.669 --> 00:26:27.679
and

00:26:27.679 --> 00:26:30.750
the

00:26:30.760 --> 00:26:34.310
foul devil of infirmity to let them go.

00:26:47.760 --> 00:26:50.070
We call

00:26:50.080 --> 00:26:53.149
them delivered by the blood

00:26:53.159 --> 00:26:54.789
of Jesus. I call their

00:27:19.360 --> 00:27:22.269
minds free from the

00:27:22.279 --> 00:27:24.870
spirit of fear

00:27:34.279 --> 00:27:36.990
and

00:27:48.830 --> 00:27:48.840
PTSD.

00:28:02.279 --> 00:28:05.350
I pray peace over their

00:28:05.360 --> 00:28:07.630
minds and call those

00:28:09.799 --> 00:28:12.830
memories of tragic events off of

00:28:12.840 --> 00:28:15.269
them.

00:28:30.960 --> 00:28:33.950
I speak life over their adrenal

00:28:33.960 --> 00:28:36.470
glands and cortisol levels;

00:28:39.120 --> 00:28:40.990
adrenal

00:28:41.000 --> 00:28:43.230
fatigue

00:28:46.029 --> 00:28:46.039
is

00:28:49.159 --> 00:28:51.830
wiped out.

00:28:59.760 --> 00:29:01.630
I call

00:29:01.640 --> 00:29:04.190
healing from cancers and tumors.

00:29:18.320 --> 00:29:21.029
We say in the name of Jesus they

00:29:21.039 --> 00:29:24.070
are delivered from diabetes,

00:29:24.070 --> 00:29:24.080
indigestion,

00:29:24.080 --> 00:29:26.710
and acid reflux.

00:29:28.389 --> 00:29:28.399
I

00:29:30.720 --> 00:29:32.909
speak

00:29:37.110 --> 00:29:37.120
to

00:29:40.559 --> 00:29:42.710
cataracts:

00:29:44.880 --> 00:29:48.029
go now in the name of Jesus. I call ears to pop open and hearing to be

00:29:48.029 --> 00:29:48.039
restored. I speak to tennis elbow, arthritis, and plantar fasciitis to

00:29:48.039 --> 00:29:51.430
go now.

00:31:24.120 --> 00:31:28.509
I call blood disorders like HIV

00:31:28.509 --> 00:31:28.519
and

00:31:28.519 --> 00:31:31.549
hepatitis healed. I bind every

00:31:31.549 --> 00:31:31.559
foul devil associated with

00:31:31.559 --> 00:31:33.509
blood

00:31:35.909 --> 00:31:35.919
disorders

00:31:38.440 --> 00:31:40.629
and

00:31:44.200 --> 00:31:49.470
command you to

00:32:00.399 --> 00:32:02.230
leave.

00:33:01.080 --> 00:33:03.950
Receive the fire of the Holy Spirit

00:33:03.950 --> 00:33:03.960
to

00:33:03.960 --> 00:33:07.230
burn

00:33:07.240 --> 00:33:10.789
out

00:33:10.799 --> 00:33:13.470
growths

00:33:13.470 --> 00:33:13.480
and

00:33:13.480 --> 00:33:16.430
tumors.

00:33:29.960 --> 00:33:33.110
I speak to that man's prostate:

00:33:36.200 --> 00:33:38.750
be healed and

00:33:38.760 --> 00:33:42.149
whole.

00:33:54.120 --> 00:33:58.789
I call

00:33:58.799 --> 00:34:01.590
restoration over female organs and

00:34:01.600 --> 00:34:04.549
the seed of man.

00:34:07.000 --> 00:34:10.470
You will conceive and

00:34:10.480 --> 00:34:14.270
receive a baby;

00:34:14.280 --> 00:34:17.430
you

00:34:17.440 --> 00:34:22.270
will not miscarry

00:34:22.270 --> 00:34:22.280
this

00:34:22.280 --> 00:34:25.310
time. It will be a full-term

00:34:25.320 --> 00:34:27.909
pregnancy.

00:35:48.119 --> 00:35:51.230
The Lord said He's

00:35:51.240 --> 00:35:54.069
going to bless your

00:35:54.079 --> 00:35:56.670
womb.

00:36:27.880 --> 00:36:31.510
Renew your mind

00:36:38.160 --> 00:36:41.030
with

00:37:02.960 --> 00:37:09.750
the

00:37:19.480 --> 00:37:21.589
Word.

00:37:29.240 --> 00:37:31.950
Thank you, Lord, for

00:37:31.960 --> 00:37:35.670
demonstrations and

00:37:35.680 --> 00:37:38.390
manifestations.

00:42:28.000 --> 00:42:30.390
We're not

00:42:30.400 --> 00:42:34.309
under the curse; Jesus has set us free.

00:42:34.319 --> 00:42:36.990
For sickness I have health, for poverty

00:42:37.000 --> 00:42:40.470
wealth, for Christ has ransomed me.

00:44:19.800 --> 00:44:22.790
In His

00:44:22.800 --> 00:44:25.470
presence,

00:44:31.839 --> 00:44:34.710
troubles

00:44:34.720 --> 00:44:37.670
vanish and hearts are

00:44:37.680 --> 00:44:40.390
mended.

00:45:46.559 --> 00:45:49.870
Reach out and grab it by faith.

00:46:33.400 --> 00:46:38.109
His name is Jesus;

00:46:41.079 --> 00:46:45.230
rise and be

00:46:45.240 --> 00:46:50.470
healed.

00:48:11.720 --> 00:48:34.230
Receive

00:49:22.240 --> 00:49:24.829
the power of the Holy Spirit

00:49:30.240 --> 00:49:33.109
now.

00:50:20.960 --> 00:50:24.710
I hope this blessed you. I

00:50:24.710 --> 00:50:24.720
had

00:50:24.720 --> 00:50:27.789
a fresh touch myself.

00:50:48.480 --> 00:50:50.750
Remember, Jesus loves you.

00:50:54.000 --> 00:50:56.670
God bless you.

